citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:50 am on
01-Feb-17.
Arrived at facility at 10:50 am. Gate locked. Called out and blew car horn. Called phone number and left call back
number request as voice mail was full. At 11:10, facility employee came to gate and informed me that the owner
was out of the country at this time. Left a business card with employee and departed.
